# Raw pixel-tileset pack (e.g. Sprout Lands by Cup Nooble — free for commercial
# use but NOT CC0). Do NOT commit the raw art to this public repo; download the
# pack into src/assets/scene/ to build locally. The built/deployed site baking the
# art into dist/ is fine — only the raw source files stay out of git.
src/assets/scene/*
!src/assets/scene/README.md

